item.title: running_checklist
item.description: Overview This is supposed to be a checklist(s) to capture race checklist items. Changelog [2021-07-31 Sat] Initial check-in, testing also some more ox-hugo stuff This is geared more towards an upcoming endurance effort. Physical [0/2]Anti-Chafe Deserves its own section as chafing is always bad Squirrel’s nut butter. Good experience with that. 2Toms products, see also: feet section. [0/2]Feet Gotta have it’s own section Leukotape P (I’ve in the past liked this).
